## 敏感操作二次验证

### 高风险操作保护

```typescript
interface SensitiveOperation {
  type: 'password_change' | 'email_change' | 'delete_account' | 'api_key_regenerate';
  requiresRecentAuth?: boolean;
}

const SENSITIVE_OPERATIONS: SensitiveOperation[] = [
  { type: 'password_change', requiresRecentAuth: true },
  { type: 'delete_account', requiresRecentAuth: true },
];

async function requireRecentAuth(env: Env, sessionId: string, maxAge: number = 5 * 60 * 1000): Promise<boolean> {
  const session = await validateSession(env, sessionId);

  if (!session) return false;

  // 检查最后认证时间
  const lastAuth = session.lastAuthAt || session.createdAt;
  return (Date.now() - lastAuth) < maxAge;
}
```

